1. How to build the native module:
1.1. npm install
1.2. npm run configure
1.3. npm run build

2. How to run unit test (mocha)
2.1 npm run mocha

3. How to run cucumber test
3.1 npm run cucumber

4. How to run node app script
4.1 npm run app

5. Results
5.1. mocha test with Promise failes
5.2. mocha test without Promise passes
5.3. cucumber step with Promise failes
5.4. cucumber step without Promise passes
5.5. node app script with or without Promise passes